    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i keep seeing the same thing over and over again like i saw a guy in a yellow jacket in chicago yesterday and then i saw him again today in a completely different city... it felt like a glitch or something. do u think im starting to hit a resource limit in the simulation? like the system is running out of assets so it's reusing them?",
